		<title>08HEALTH</title>
		<content>       We have a surgery in our area   
 and a hospital for the old age.       
       Outside our area we have the    
 town hospital.It is not a major       
 hospital but you can have             
 minor surgery there.All major         
 operations are carried out at either  
 Singleton hospital,Swansea or Neath   
 general.                              
       The general health of the       
 overall population has been at risk   
 for many years due to the never ending
 pollution from the steelworks.Even    
 though the enviromental controls have 
 improved in recent years,air pollution
 is still a problem.                   
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
